Key obligations under this tier:

  1. You MUST provide the complete corresponding source code to any derivative
     works, whether distributed as source or binary form.

  2. You CANNOT close the source of any part of the L.I.L.I.E.T.H. Kernel.
     Any fork, port, or derivative of the LILIETH kernel logic must remain
